translated: Bielke, Nils, Count, Sturefors, b. 29/7/17 in Sturefors, Östergötland. Son of Master of the Horse, Count Thure Gabriel B. and Brita Sparre. Attended Svalöv's farmer school, studied at Oxford in 1937. Head of the Bielke family. Owns the ancestral estates of Sturefors, Viggebyholm, Slattefors, Ähagen, and Briteborg, all located in Östergötland. Married (date of marriage unknown).
